(324, 1500, 1999, 'honda', 'accord', 'good', '6 cylinders', 'gas', '211000', 'clean', 'automatic', 'fwd', 5, '', 'sedan', 'black', 'https://images.craigslist.org/00d0d_141WpPeH2dp_600x450.jpg', 'This right here is 1999 Honda Accord. Have you ever heard of the legendary reliability AK-47 assault rifle? This vehicular awesomeness is basically the automobile analog to the AK-47̢????s inability to fail. It̢????s 20-years-old but it doesn̢????t have the temperament of a 20-year-old human. It̢????s not neurotic, whiney, or unsure of what it wants. It̢????s more of a gruff old man who knows his role and knows his place and doesn̢????t whine and complain about anything; he just does what he needs to do. He ain̢????t pretty and he isn̢????t gonna give you a sensual massage. But let̢????s be honest, you̢????re looking into this car because you can̢????t afford a Ferrari and you don̢????t want to have to deal with all the stupid problems that come from a lesser, better-looking car. This baby is meant to go from A to B as quickly and reliably as possible and that̢????s it. Or you could rip out its invincible engine and put it in an ultra 4 truck or some other racing vehicle and absolutely smoke the competition. Now let̢????s talk about the sweeter-than-honey things about this car and the not-so-sweeter-than-honey things about this car.\n\nSweeter-than-honey:\nAs mentioned before, it̢????s an AK-47 and more reliable than 98% of the other garbage on here.\nIt̢????s got a sweet 6-cylinder engine that goes 0-60 so quick that any cops that catch you won̢????t know whether to write you a ticket or congratulate this ugly son-of-a-gun for being so fast. They̢????ll probably write you a ticket anyway, but hey that̢????s the risk you take when driving this beast.\nIt̢????s got an A/C that̢????ll have you shivering in 110???? Texas heat in no time. (This is sweeter-than-honey because of a not-so-sweeter-than-honey feature but we̢????ll get there).\nIt has front-wheel-drive which means you